data.description: Motivated Seller, 3 bedroom/2bathroom home with lots of potential. Oversized Fenced lot, Roof replaced in 2007, impact windows installed 2008, impact garage door installed 2007, impact front door in 2018, electric range and dishwasher from 2016, and AC replaced in 2012. Room addition permitted and can be used as a family room/office . New bathroom tile, water heater, and light fixtures available, just need to be installed! HOA extremely low at 33$ a month. Showings and more pictures will be available starting Tuesday (1/23/2024), submit best offer!
